plugins.mantis.description: Enable your team to report a bug on Mantis Bug Tracker, track status and rerun on closure of bug without leaving Testsigma from the test case results page.
plugins.freshrelease.description: Enable your team to report a bug on Freshrelease, track status and rerun on closure of bug without leaving Testsigma from the test case results page.
plugins.backLog.description: Enable your team to report a bug on Backlog, track status and rerun on closue of bug without leaving Testsigma from the test case results page.
plugins.zepel.description: Enable your team to report a bug on Zepel, track status and rerun on closure of bug without leaving Testsigma from the test case results page.
plugins.bugzilla.description: Enable your team to report a bug on BugZilla, track status and rerun on closure of bug without leaving Testsigma from the test case results page.
plugins.trello.description: Enable your team to report a bug on Trello, track status and rerun on closure of bug without leaving Testsigma from the test case results page.
plugins.description.azureDevOps: Azure DevOps has robust integrations with Azure and a comprehensive suite of technologies that help you deliver software securely and quickly. Combine Azure DevOps with Testsigma to match your unique workflow, then seamlessly integrate them on Azure.
plugins.azure.description: Enable your team to report a bug on Azure DevOps Boards, track status and rerun on closure of bug without leaving Testsigma from the test case results page.
plugins.description.circleCI: CircleCI allows teams to rapidly release code they trust by automating the build, test, and delivery process for both mobile and web apps. Testsigma offers seamless integration with CircleCI.
plugins.description.bamboo: By integrating Testsigma application with Bamboo, you can seamlessly view and monitor the status of your Bamboo builds and deployments without leaving your Testsigma projects.
plugins.description.aws: Utilise the power of AWS Cloud by integrating your Testsigma application with Amazon Web Services.
plugins.description.travisCI: Travis CI enables your team to test and ship your apps with confidence. Easily sync your Testsigma projects with Travis CI and you'll be testing your code in minutes.
plugins.description.jenkins: Integration of Jenkins with Testsigma helps you to run your scripts whenever there is a change in software code. Jenkins helps to schedule your build to run the test cases from a batch file, save your test reports and the execution history.
plugins.description.code_ship: Codeship helps to release software quickly, automatically and multiple times a day. It integrates with Testsigma, automatically deploying when tests pass and notifying you when tests or deployments have failed.
plugins.linear.description: Enable your team to report a bug on Linear, track status and rerun on closure of bug without leaving Testsigma from test case results page.
plugins.youtrack.description: Enable your team to report a bug on YouTrack, track status and rerun on closure of bug without leaving Testsigma from the test case results page.
plugins.testsigma_lab.description: Connect to your Tesigma Lab account as your test lab on cloud.
plugins.private_lab.description: Connect to your Private Selenium Grid Lab / Appium Grid account as your test lab on cloud.
